msgid_plural "Elijah's holomessages"
msgstr[0] "以利亞的全息留言"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Elijah's holomessage"}
#: .\items\books.json
msgid ""
"A holotape containing pre-recorded message from Elijah to someone named "
"Veronica. You can't understand much but it sounds like a father saying "
"goodbye to his daughter."
msgstr "一段全息磁帶，內含以利亞給一位名叫維羅妮卡之人的預錄信息。你聽不太懂具體內容，但聽起來像是一位父親在向女兒道別。"

