msgstr "一件淺灰色連體服，類似於技術工人穿著的款式。但與那些不同，這件背後有一個紅色十字標記。"

#: .\items\clothes.json
msgid "Father Elijah's robe"
msgid_plural "Father Elijah's robes"
msgstr[0] "以利亞神父的長袍"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Father Elijah's robe"}
#: .\items\clothes.json
msgid ""
"Long, dark-blue robes, apparently belonging to Father Elijah. They appear "
