#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"Bear trap fist upgraded with HD strings for easier and more firm strapping "
"onto the user's shoulder, allowing to deal more powerful blows. It has been "
"poisoned with the venom made out of the Sierra Madre Cloud and thanks to it "
"will poison your enemies, dealing additional damage over time."
msgstr ""
"捕熊陷阱拳套升級了高清綁帶，便於更牢固地固定在用戶肩部，從而能造成更強大的打擊。它已被馬德雷山脈雲霧製成的毒液淬毒，因此能毒害你的敵人，造成持續額外傷害。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "upgraded bear trap fist poisoned with Cloud Kiss (potent)"
msgid_plural "upgraded bear trap fists poisoned with Cloud Kiss (potent)"
msgstr[0] "塗有雲吻之毒（強效）的升級版捕熊陷阱拳套"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "upgraded bear trap fist poisoned with Cloud Kiss (lethal)"
msgid_plural "upgraded bear trap fists poisoned with Cloud Kiss (lethal)"
msgstr[0] "塗有雲吻之毒（致命）的升級版捕熊陷阱拳套"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "cosmic knife"
msgid_plural "cosmic knives"
msgstr[0] "宇宙刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cosmic knife', 'str_pl': 'cosmic knives'}
#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"The state-of-tech steak knife made out of advanced steel alloys developed at"
" Big Mountain research facility shortly before the apocalypse. Makes an "
"excellent weapon, to the point you wonder who and how at Big Mountain made a"
" mistake of designing it as a civilian steak knife before introducing it to "
"the military as a new combat knife."
msgstr ""
"採用大山脈研究設施在末世前不久研發的先進鋼合金製成的科技牛排刀。作為武器表現卓越，以至於你會疑惑大山脈的何人在何種情況下，竟在將其作為新型戰鬥刀引入軍方之前，錯誤地將其設計為民用牛排刀。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "cosmic knife poisoned with Cloud Kiss (weak)"
msgid_plural "cosmic knives poisoned with Cloud Kiss (weak)"
msgstr[0] "塗有雲吻之毒（弱效）的宇宙刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cosmic knife poisoned with Cloud Kiss (weak)',
#. 'str_pl': 'cosmic knives poisoned with Cloud Kiss (weak)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cosmic knife poisoned with Cloud Kiss (potent)',
#. 'str_pl': 'cosmic knives poisoned with Cloud Kiss (potent)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cosmic knife poisoned with Cloud Kiss (lethal)',
#. 'str_pl': 'cosmic knives poisoned with Cloud Kiss (lethal)'}
#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"The state-of-tech steak knife made out of advanced steel alloys developed at"
" Big Mountain research facility shortly before the apocalypse. Makes an "
"excellent weapon, to the point you wonder who and how at Big Mountain made a"
" mistake of designing it as a civilian steak knife before introducing it to "
"the military as a new combat knife. It has been poisoned with the venom made"
" out of the Sierra Madre Cloud and thanks to it will poison your enemies, "
"dealing additional damage over time."
msgstr ""
"採用大山脈研究設施在末世前不久研發的先進鋼合金製成的科技牛排刀。作為武器表現卓越，以至於你會疑惑大山脈的何人在何種情況下，竟在將其作為新型戰鬥刀引入軍方之前，錯誤地將其設計為民用牛排刀。它已被馬德雷山脈雲霧製成的毒液淬毒，因此能毒害你的敵人，造成持續額外傷害。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "cosmic knife poisoned with Cloud Kiss (potent)"
msgid_plural "cosmic knives poisoned with Cloud Kiss (potent)"
msgstr[0] "塗有雲吻之毒（強效）的宇宙刀"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "cosmic knife poisoned with Cloud Kiss (lethal)"
msgid_plural "cosmic knives poisoned with Cloud Kiss (lethal)"
msgstr[0] "塗有雲吻之毒（致命）的宇宙刀"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "clean cosmic knife"
msgid_plural "clean cosmic knives"
msgstr[0] "潔淨宇宙刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'clean cosmic knife', 'str_pl': 'clean cosmic
#. knives'}
#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"A cosmic knife polished with common detergents and other household cleaning "
"products. It's shiny... And deadly. Its bright, shiny surface could "
"metaphorically represent your hope of survivng the Sierra Madre."
msgstr "用普通清潔劑和其他家用清潔產品拋光過的宇宙刀。它閃閃發光……且致命。其明亮閃亮的表面或許能象徵性地代表你在馬德雷山脈生存的希望。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "super-heated cosmic knife"
msgid_plural "super-heated cosmic knives"
msgstr[0] "超熱宇宙刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'super-heated cosmic knife', 'str_pl': 'super-
#. heated cosmic knives'}
#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"A cosmic knife heated up to an extreme temperature. As accidentially "
"discovered by one of the Sierra Madre chefs, its handle remains cool, "
"allowing you to wield it and burn your foes. Now your hope for surving "
"Sierra Madre is burning just like this blade."
msgstr ""
"一把加熱到極高溫的宇宙之刃。正如塞拉馬德雷的一位廚師偶然發現的那樣，它的刀柄保持涼爽，讓你能夠揮舞它並灼燒敵人。如今，你在塞拉馬德雷求生的希望，正如這把刀刃般熊熊燃燒。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "Ghost's gas bomb"
msgid_plural "Ghost's gas bombs"
msgstr[0] "幽靈的氣體炸彈"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': "Ghost's gas bomb"}.
#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "Activate"
msgstr "激活"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': "Ghost's gas bomb"}.
#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "You activate the bomb's igniter."
msgstr "你啟動了炸彈的點火器。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Ghost's gas bomb"}
#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"A small tank full of highly-flammable gas repurposed to serve as a makeshift"
" bomb, ready to explode in a blaze of glory. Also it seems as if the Sierra "
"Madre toxins were added to the mixture..."
msgstr "一個裝滿高度易燃氣體的小罐子，被改造成臨時炸彈，準備在榮耀的烈焰中爆炸。此外，混合物中似乎還添加了塞拉馬德雷的毒素……"

#. ~ Use action no_deactivate_msg for {'str': "Ghost's gas bomb"}.
#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"The sharp, hissing sound coming out of the tank indicates the blaze of glory"
" is about to be unleashed to wipe the Sierra Madre clean... Well, at least "
"\"some part of it\", technically speaking."
msgstr "罐子發出的尖銳嘶嘶聲預示著榮耀的烈焰即將釋放，將塞拉馬德雷清掃一空……好吧，嚴格來說，至少是“它的某一部分”。"

#. ~ Use action sound_msg for {'str': "Ghost's gas bomb"}.
#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "Psfft."
msgstr "嘶——"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Ghost's gas bomb"}
#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"Throw this bomb quickly and run away before the blaze of glory consumes you!"
msgstr "快扔出這顆炸彈，在榮耀的烈焰吞噬你之前逃跑！"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "holorifle"
msgid_plural "holorifles"
msgstr[0] "全息步槍"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"A state-of-tech gun, the holorifle is a very powerful pump-action rifle "
"firing holobeams, utilizing microfusion cells. Holds four rounds in its "
"internal, tube-shaped magazine and is quite reliable, though thanks to it "
"being an improvised technology can still jam sometimes, especially when "
"using overcharged cells. Comes with its own unique scope attached that is "
"pleasant to look through, allowing good aiming precision, as well as a "
"shoulder strap."
msgstr ""
"一把科技前沿的槍械，全息步槍是一種非常強大的泵動式步槍，發射全息光束，使用微型聚變電池供能。其內置管狀彈匣可容納四發彈藥，相當可靠，但由於是臨時拼湊的技術，有時仍會卡殼，尤其是在使用過充電池時。附帶一個獨特的瞄準鏡，視野清晰，瞄準精度高，還配有肩帶。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "pump-action"
msgstr "泵動式"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "chuk chuk."
msgstr "咔嚓咔嚓。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "Gauss rifle"
msgid_plural "Gauss rifles"
msgstr[0] "高斯步槍"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"An experimental energetic marksman rifle, utilizing microfusion cells to "
"accelerate conductive or ferromagnetic projectiles to insane speed. This "
"model is fed with a special packs of 5 microfusion cells, discharging all of"
" them during one shot, effectively making it a single-shot weapon at a price"
" of 5 rounds per shot. The accuracy and damage are worth it, though."
msgstr ""
"一把實驗性的高能射手步槍，利用微型聚變電池將導電或鐵磁彈丸加速到驚人的速度。此型號使用特殊的5發微型聚變電池包供彈，每射擊一次會耗盡全部電池，實際上使其成為單發武器，代價是每發消耗5發彈藥。不過，其精準度和傷害是值得的。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "single-shot"
msgstr "單發"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "slosh."
msgstr "晃動。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "laser pistol"
msgid_plural "laser pistols"
msgstr[0] "激光手槍"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"A next-gen laser pistol prototype, firing energy cells from its 30-round "
"magazine designed specifically for it. Unlike other energy weapons, it needs"
" a special ammo rather than just a power supply, but the power it gives in "
"return was deemed worth it by its engineers at Big Mountain research "
"facility. Unfortunately, occassionally can jam."
msgstr ""
"一款次世代激光手槍原型，從其專為它設計的30發彈匣中發射能量電池。與其他能量武器不同，它需要特殊彈藥而非僅靠電源供能，但其工程師在大山研究設施認為其回報的威力是值得的。不幸的是，偶爾會卡殼。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "semi-auto"
msgstr "半自動"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "Colt Trooper .357 Magnum"
msgid_plural "Colt Trooper .357 Magnum"
msgstr[0] "柯爾特騎兵 .357 馬格南"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid ""
"Introduced in 1953, this revolver features pretty good weight and "
"comfortable handling. It came with Target version for sport shooting and "
"Service for law enforcement officers, the latter complaining about weight of"
" their sidearms before. This particular model is the high-end .357 Magnum "
"version, capable of firing .38 Special as well."
msgstr ""
"這款左輪手槍於1953年推出，重量適中，握持舒適。它提供用於體育射擊的Target版和供執法官員使用的Service版，後者此前曾抱怨其配槍過重。此特定型號是高端.357馬格南版本，也能發射.38特種彈。"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "Hologram laser beam"
msgid_plural "Hologram laser beams"
msgstr[0] "全息激光束"

#: .\items\weapons.json
msgid "A laser beam used by Sierra Madre security holograms."
msgstr "塞拉馬德雷安全全息影像使用的激光束。"

