#: .\monsters\ghosts.json
msgid "Ghost harvester"
msgid_plural "Ghost harvesters"
msgstr[0] "幽靈收割者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ghost harvester'}
#: .\monsters\ghosts.json
msgid ""
"A smaller and weaker type of Ghost People, though still very deadly due to "
"high agility. Fights using knife spears, both in melee and throwing them "
"from a distance."
msgstr "一種體型較小、較弱的幽靈人類型，但由於高敏捷性仍然非常致命。使用刀矛戰鬥，既可近戰也可遠距離投擲。"

#: .\monsters\ghosts.json
msgid "The Ghost harvester throws a knife spear!"
msgstr "幽靈收割者投擲了一把刀矛！"

#: .\monsters\ghosts.json
msgid "Ghost trapper"
msgid_plural "Ghost trappers"
msgstr[0] "幽靈陷阱者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ghost trapper'}
#: .\monsters\ghosts.json
msgid ""
"This Ghost has a large, bulky body yet still maintains a great degree of "
"agility. Armed with a small bear trap strapped to its arm, will try to claw "
"at you using it."
msgstr "這種幽靈擁有龐大笨重的身體，但仍保持高度的敏捷性。裝備著綁在手臂上的小型捕熊夾，會試圖用它來抓撓你。"

#: .\monsters\ghosts.json
msgid "Ghost seeker"
msgid_plural "Ghost seekers"
msgstr[0] "幽靈搜尋者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ghost seeker'}
#: .\monsters\ghosts.json
msgid ""
"Taller than harvesters, weaker and skinnier than trappers, those Ghosts will"
" often throw an improvised gas bomb before engaging with their knife spears,"
" making them a potentially deadly enemies. If you survive the blast though, "
"they'll be easier to deal with than trappers for sure."
msgstr ""
"比收割者更高，比陷阱者更弱更瘦，這些幽靈在近身使用刀矛戰鬥前，通常會投擲簡易氣體炸彈，使它們成為潛在的致命敵人。不過，如果你能在爆炸中倖存，它們肯定比陷阱者更容易對付。"

#: .\monsters\ghosts.json
msgid "The Ghost seeker throws its gas bomb!"
msgstr "幽靈搜尋者投擲了它的氣體炸彈！"

#: .\monsters\holograms.json
msgid "Sierra Madre security hologram"
msgid_plural "Sierra Madre security holograms"
msgstr[0] "馬德雷山脈安全全息影像"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sierra Madre security hologram'}
#: .\monsters\holograms.json
msgid ""
"One of the greatest Big Mountain achievements, this hologram is far more "
"than just display - it's capable of detecting hostile targets and firing its"
" internal laser beam at them. Completely invincible, so don't waste your "
"ammo and whatever other combat supplies you might have. Can only be switched"
" off if you find and access its emitter."
msgstr ""
"大山脈最偉大的成就之一，這個全息影像遠不止是展示——它能夠檢測敵對目標並向其發射內部激光束。完全無敵，所以不要浪費你的彈藥和其他任何戰鬥物資。只有找到並訪問其發射器才能關閉它。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sierra Madre security hologram'}
#: .\monsters\holograms.json
msgid ""
"One of the greatest Big Mountain achievements, this hologram is far more "
"than just display - it's capable of detecting hostile targets and firing its"
" internal laser beam at them. Completely invincible, so don't waste your "
"ammo and whatever other combat supplies you might have. Can only be switched"
" off if you find and access its emitter. This one act as a friendly immobile"
" sentry though, since it was you who took control of it."
msgstr ""
"大山脈最偉大的成就之一，這個全息影像遠不止是展示——它能夠檢測敵對目標並向其發射內部激光束。完全無敵，所以不要浪費你的彈藥和其他任何戰鬥物資。只有找到並訪問其發射器才能關閉它。不過這個作為友好的固定哨兵，因為是你控制了它。"

#: .\monsters\holograms.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Vera Keyes' hologram"
msgid_plural "Sierra Madre Vera Keyes' holograms"
msgstr[0] "馬德雷山脈薇拉·凱斯全息影像"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Sierra Madre Vera Keyes' hologram"}
#: .\monsters\holograms.json
msgid ""
"One of the greatest Big Mountain achievements, this hologram is far more "
"than just display - it's capable of detecting hostile targets and firing its"
" internal laser beam at them. Completely invincible, so don't waste your "
"ammo and whatever other combat supplies you might have. Can only be switched"
" off if you find and access its emitter. This one seems to have taken the "
"form of Vera Keyes for some strange reason."
msgstr ""
"大山脈最偉大的成就之一，這個全息影像遠不止是展示——它能夠檢測敵對目標並向其發射內部激光束。完全無敵，所以不要浪費你的彈藥和其他任何戰鬥物資。只有找到並訪問其發射器才能關閉它。這個似乎因某種奇怪原因呈現為薇拉·凱斯的形態。"

#: .\monsters\speech.json
msgid "HHAAAARRRRRR"
msgstr "哈啊啊啊啊啊啊"

#: .\monsters\speech.json
msgid "HHUUUURRRR"
msgstr "呼嗚嗚嗚嗚"

#: .\monsters\speech.json
msgid "HHEEEEEHH"
msgstr "嘿誒誒誒誒"

#: .\monsters\speech.json
msgid "HHOOOORHH"
msgstr "吼嗚嗚嗚"

#: .\monsters\speech.json
msgid "HAARRRHHH"
msgstr "哈啊啊啊"

#: .\monsters\speech.json
msgid ""
"Sinclair?! Sinclair, I'm trapped. Please, oh god, the security systems won't"
" let me out, they're keeping me here."
msgstr "辛克萊？！辛克萊，我被困住了。求你了，天哪，安全系統不讓我出去，它們把我關在這裡。"

#: .\monsters\speech.json
msgid "Sinclair?! SINCLAIR!!!"
msgstr "辛克萊？！辛克萊！！！"

#: .\monsters\speech.json
msgid ""
"We all pay for what we've done. I'm so sorry, Sinclair. Sorry, I... I should"
" have trusted you."
msgstr "我們都為自己所做的事付出代價。我很抱歉，辛克萊。對不起，我……我應該相信你的。"

#: .\monsters\speech.json
msgid ""
"I'm going to die here, amongst the ghosts. I... I'm still being recorded by "
"the holographic system."
msgstr "我要死在這裡了，在幽靈之中。我……我仍然被全息系統記錄著。"

#: .\monsters\speech.json
msgid ""
"The doors, they... they sealed. I... I can hear the other guests, screaming "
"to be let out, to let go."
msgstr "門，它們……它們封死了。我……我能聽到其他客人在尖叫，要求被放出去，要求放手。"

#: .\monsters\speech.json
msgid "Let go? Let go of what?"
msgstr "放手？放下什麼？"

#: .\monsters\speech.json
msgid ""
"I came so far to be here... Now, now I just want to leave. Please... Let me "
"leave."
msgstr "我千里迢迢來到這裡……現在，現在我只想離開。求求你……讓我離開。"

#: .\monsters\speech.json
msgid ""
"Sinclair? Sinclair, where did you go? Why did you leave me here? Why..."
msgstr "辛克萊？辛克萊，你去哪兒了？為什麼把我留在這裡？為什麼……"

#: .\monsters\speech.json
msgid "Sinclair, is that you?"
msgstr "辛克萊，是你嗎？"

#: .\monsters\turrets.json
msgid "laser turret"
msgid_plural "laser turrets"
msgstr[0] "激光炮塔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'laser turret'}
#: .\monsters\turrets.json
msgid ""
"A simple military-grade laser turret for protecting important areas. Nothing"
" too special about it, but it's deadly and gets the job done."
msgstr "一種簡單的軍用級激光炮塔，用於保護重要區域。它沒什麼特別之處，但致命且能完成任務。"

#: .\monsters\turrets.json
msgid "broken laser turret"
msgid_plural "broken laser turrets"
msgstr[0] "損壞的激光炮塔"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Casino Locator Hologram"
msgstr "馬德雷賭場定位器全息圖"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Hologram Protection"
msgstr "全息影像防護"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hologram Protection'}
#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "\"I am programmed to not engage wandering monsters.\""
msgstr "\"我的程序設定為不與遊蕩怪物交戰。\""

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Go to Sierra Madre Casino'}'
#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Go to Sierra Madre Casino"
msgstr "前往馬德雷賭場"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"You want me to find this location for you to explore? Sure, you will just "
"need to wait for a couple of minutes or less for me to find it via my "
"network system"
msgstr "要我為你定位探索地點？沒問題，只需等我用網絡系統查找幾分鐘或更短時間"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"You want me to locate it now for you to explore? Sure, just tell me, you "
"will just need to wait for a couple of minutes or less for me to find it via"
" my network system"
msgstr "你想讓我現在為你定位那個地點以便探索嗎？當然，告訴我吧，你只需要等幾分鐘或更短時間，我就能通過網絡系統找到它。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Good luck to you!"
msgstr "祝你好運！"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"Not interested in explorations of new locations? No rush hopefully. You can "
"come back to me later. I'm sure that you will. Because I believe that you "
"are not a boring person"
msgstr "對新地點的探索不感興趣嗎？別急，希望如此。你可以稍後再來找我。我相信你會的，因為我覺得你不是個無聊的人。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Use your wits for your own safety hopefully as well"
msgstr "也希望你運用智慧確保自身安全。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Have you went to this location that I have found for you to explore?"
msgstr "你去過我為你找到的那個探索地點了嗎？"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Good work!"
msgstr "幹得好！"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"What's the point of lying to me? You think I'm gonna reward you? Your "
"rewards for this mission is valuable for you items or living creatures or "
"other survivors you manage to find in this location which I have found for "
"you to explore"
msgstr ""
"對我撒謊有什麼意義？你以為我會獎勵你嗎？這次任務的獎勵就是你在那個地點找到的對你來說有價值的物品、生物或其他倖存者，那是我為你找到的探索地點。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"You are a boring, lazy person honestly. I guess that laziness applies to "
"both of us"
msgstr "說實話，你是個無聊又懶惰的人。我想懶惰這一點我們倆都適用。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"System is online. Initiate conversation mode. Look at that. Survivor has "
"managed to activate a hologram projector easily! Yeah, my creators know many"
" types of you who don't even read what's written on items honestly. Good "
"that you seem like a pretty intelligent person hopefully. So, do you want me"
" to show you where this location is via my network system? I can grant you "
"access to archived global network system which my creators have managed to "
"restore. However, after usage I will need to recharge a little bit which "
"only means that you will need to wait to use this function again hopefully"
msgstr ""
"系統在線。啟動對話模式。看啊，倖存者輕鬆激活了全息投影儀！沒錯，我的創造者瞭解很多像你這樣的人，說實話他們甚至不讀物品上的說明。幸好你看起來是個相當聰明的人，希望如此。那麼，你想讓我通過網絡系統為你顯示這個地點的位置嗎？我可以授予你訪問存檔全球網絡系統的權限，那是我的創造者設法恢復的。不過，使用後我需要稍微充能，這意味著你需要等待才能再次使用這個功能，希望如此。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"[MISSIONS] I want you to find this location for me to explore it hopefully "
"via your network system"
msgstr "[任務] 我希望你通過你的網絡系統為我找到這個地點以便探索，希望如此。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Who or what are you?"
msgstr "你是誰或是什麼東西？"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"Who are your creators? What is the purpose of producing these projectors?"
msgstr "你的創造者是誰？製造這些投影儀的目的是什麼？"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"[IMPROVE MOOD] I want you to grant me access to archived global network "
"system"
msgstr "[改善心情] 我希望你授予我訪問存檔全球網絡系統的權限。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "About that mission..."
msgstr "關於那個任務……"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "[GOODBYE]"
msgstr "[告別]"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"Initiate search mode. Please, wait for a couple of minutes or less. You've "
"heard me clearly. Still, we have limitations with regards to our locating "
"tools. If locator does not manage to find this location then simply create "
"another hologram locator of which can find this location successfully"
msgstr ""
"啟動搜索模式。請等待幾分鐘或更短時間。你聽清楚了。不過，我們的定位工具有所限制。如果定位器無法找到這個地點，那就簡單地創建另一個能成功找到該地點的全息定位器。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Can I talk to you about something else?"
msgstr "我能和你談談別的嗎？"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "Thanks"
msgstr "謝謝。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"I'm a magic genie from a magic camera. No, I'm just joking. What kind of a "
"question is this? You don't like to explore or don't know much about your "
"own world? Have not you seen stuff in labs? Military structures? Top secret "
"stuff? Aliens or whatever these creatures are? You think that your own "
"people don't have tech which can produce holograms? I'm a hologram, software"
" with some additional technologies, it is that simple"
msgstr ""
"我是魔法相機裡的魔法精靈。不，開個玩笑。這是什麼問題？你不喜歡探索，還是對自己的世界瞭解不多？你沒在實驗室裡見過東西嗎？軍事設施？絕密物品？外星人或那些生物？你以為你們自己人沒有能製造全息影像的技術嗎？我是個全息影像，是帶有附加技術的軟件，就這麼簡單。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"This question is much more intelligent than the other one. My creators can "
"be described as a bunch of highly technological geeks majority of which are "
"humans honestly. They neither possess that many combat skills nor they are "
"that interested in subjecting their lives to unnecessary risk clearly. They "
"only engage hostile creatures for basic survival needs. They try to rely on "
"self-sufficiency with relative success thanks to their applied intelligence "
"along with tech that they have managed to find or engineer themselves. They "
"have made these projectors so that we can help each other. We provide you "
"with locations with dangerous creatures along with valuable items or "
"survivors who are captive. You clear these locations acquiring whatever "
"valuable items or survivors you want from there making these locations safe "
"shelters where we including you can live hopefully as well"
msgstr ""
"這個問題比上一個聰明多了。我的創造者可以說是一群高科技極客，說實話其中大多數是人類。他們既沒有太多戰鬥技能，也顯然不願讓自己的生命承受不必要的風險。他們只會在基本生存需要時與敵對生物交戰。他們試圖依靠自給自足，並憑藉應用智慧和自行發現或設計的技術取得相對成功。他們製造這些投影儀是為了我們能互相幫助。我們為你提供有危險生物的地點，以及有價值的物品或被囚禁的倖存者。你清理這些地點，從中獲取你想要的任何有價值物品或倖存者，使這些地點成為安全的庇護所，希望我們包括你也能在那裡生活。"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"What do you want to do? Play archived games? Browse archived social media? "
"Watch archived videos? Listen to archived music? Read archived files along "
"with archived books? Something to play, read, listen, watch for fun, "
"intelligence improving, spiritual improving, mental improving?"
msgstr ""
"你想做什麼？玩存檔遊戲？瀏覽存檔社交媒體？看存檔視頻？聽存檔音樂？閱讀存檔文件和存檔書籍？找點東西玩、讀、聽、看，為了樂趣、提升智力、精神提升、心智改善？"

#: .\npcs\NPC_missions.json
msgid "I like some of these a lot honestly. Healthy stuff"
msgstr "說實話，我很喜歡其中一些。健康的東西。"

#: .\npcs\consoles.json
msgid "Sierra Madre Vault main terminal"
msgstr "馬德雷金庫主終端"

#. ~ Description for vault control terminal
#: .\npcs\consoles.json .\terrain\furniture.json
msgid ""
"Still operational terminal inside the Sierra Madre Vault, providing access "
"to the most important data for Frederick Sinclair."
msgstr "馬德雷金庫內仍可運行的終端，為弗雷德裡克·辛克萊提供最重要數據的訪問權限。"

#: .\npcs\consoles.json .\terrain\furniture.json
msgid "vault control terminal"
msgstr "金庫控制終端"

#: .\npcs\consoles.json .\npcs\dialogue_gala.json .\terrain\furniture.json
msgid "Gala control panel"
msgstr "慶典控制面板"

#: .\npcs\consoles.json
msgid "Main terminal for controlling the Gala Event."
msgstr "控制慶典活動的主終端。"

#: .\npcs\consoles.json
msgid "power control terminal"
msgstr "電力控制終端"

#. ~ Description for Power control terminal
#: .\npcs\consoles.json .\terrain\furniture.json
msgid ""
"Still operational terminal used to manually control the power of the inner "
"systems in the Sierra Madre Casino."
msgstr "仍可運行的終端，用於手動控制馬德雷賭場內部系統的電力。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_casino_power.json .\terrain\furniture.json
msgid "Power control terminal"
msgstr "電力控制終端"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_casino_power.json
msgid "Manually restore casino's power"
msgstr "手動恢復賭場電力"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_casino_power.json .\npcs\dialogue_console.json
#: .\npcs\dialogue_gala.json .\npcs\dialogue_vendor.json
msgid "Exit"
msgstr "退出"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_casino_power.json
msgid "Power systems online..."
msgstr "電力系統在線..."

#: .\npcs\dialogue_casino_vendor.json
msgid "Welcome to the Sierra Madre Casino. Would you like to buy some chips?"
msgstr "歡迎來到馬德雷賭場。您想買些籌碼嗎？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_casino_vendor.json
msgid "Yes."
msgstr "是的。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_casino_vendor.json .\npcs\dialogue_vendor.json
msgid "No thanks, I think I have to go."
msgstr "不用了，謝謝，我想我得走了。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_casino_vendor.json
msgid ""
"We hope you're satisfied with the transaction and wish you good luck. "
"Anything else we can do for you?"
msgstr "希望您對交易滿意，祝您好運。還有什麼我們能為您做的嗎？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_casino_vendor.json .\npcs\dialogue_vendor.json
msgid "No, that's all."
msgstr "不，就這些了。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_casino_vendor.json
msgid "Yes, I'd like to buy some more."
msgstr "是的，我想再買一些。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"Wait! Who the hell are you? What the hell are you even doing here?! How... "
"How... Nobody, since the Courier, (God/Dog) and Dean left... Nobody..."
msgstr "等等！你他媽是誰？你他媽到底在這裡幹什麼？！怎麼...怎麼...自從信使、（上帝/狗）和迪恩離開後...沒人..."

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid "No, who the hell are YOU! What the hell are YOU even doing here?!"
msgstr "不，你他媽是誰！你他媽到底在這裡幹什麼？！"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid "Step aside... Madre's mine mine mine!!!!!!!!!"
msgstr "讓開...馬德雷是我的我的我的!!!!!!!!!"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid "You speak like Vera Keyes..."
msgstr "你說話像薇拉·凱斯..."

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid "Alright, calm down and let's talk this over"
msgstr "好吧，冷靜下來，我們談談"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid "What the hell is going here? Why are you standing here?"
msgstr "這裡到底發生了什麼？你為什麼站在這裡？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"No... You don't understand. I can't let you in... That's my job. To protect "
"the world from him. From the Sierra Madre and it's curse of greed and "
"neediness as a whole. If you enter the vault... No, you can't enter the "
"vault. You shouldn't have come here."
msgstr ""
"不...你不明白。我不能讓你進去...那是我的工作。保護世界免受他的傷害。免受馬德雷及其貪婪與匱乏的詛咒。如果你進入金庫...不，你不能進入金庫。你不該來這裡。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"NO! I WON'T PLAY STUPID GAMES! MADRE'S MINE MINE "
"MINE!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!"
msgstr "不！我不會玩愚蠢的遊戲！馬德雷是我的我的我的!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"Why not? I came so far. I went through so much. I can't leave. I'm not "
"letting go. Not now."
msgstr "為什麼不？我走了這麼遠。我經歷了這麼多。我不能離開。我不會放手。現在不行。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"I... I'm guarding the Sierra Madre. To protect the world from it. I was "
"trapped. Together with Dean, (Dog/God) and the Courier. The four of us... "
"All enslaved... Father Elijah forced us to work for him to break into the "
"vault, then told the Courier to kill us all... But Courier was a human, not "
"a monster. The Courier saved us all."
msgstr ""
"我……我在守衛錫耶拉馬德雷。為了保護世界免受其害。我被困住了。和迪恩、(狗/神)還有信使一起。我們四個……全都被奴役了……以利亞神父強迫我們為他工作，闖入金庫，然後命令信使殺掉我們所有人……但信使是人，不是怪物。信使救了我們所有人。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid "Did... Did he use collars to force obedience?"
msgstr "他……他是用項圈來強迫服從的嗎？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid "What can you tell me about the Courier, (Dog/God) and Dean Domino?"
msgstr "關於信使、(狗/神)和迪恩·多米諾，你能告訴我些什麼？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid "What happened to the Father Elijah?"
msgstr "以利亞神父後來怎麼樣了？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"Dean Domino was planning this heist himself, long before the rest of us saw "
"the Sierra Madre walls... He forced me into one of the villa's clinic "
"autodocs to operate my voice... So that, upon figuring out the password, he "
"could use me to unlock the vault..."
msgstr ""
"迪恩·多米諾自己策劃了這次搶劫，遠在我們其他人看到錫耶拉馬德雷的圍牆之前……他強迫我進入別墅診所的一臺自動醫療機，對我的聲音進行手術……這樣，在破解密碼後，他就能利用我來打開金庫……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid "I'm sorry you had to go through this..."
msgstr "很抱歉你不得不經歷這些……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"Okay, so, to sum up our current situation, I'm here guarding the Sierra "
"Madre and you came here... You should leave. There's nothing awaiting you in"
" the Sierra Madre."
msgstr "好吧，那麼，總結一下我們目前的情況，我在這裡守衛錫耶拉馬德雷，而你來到了這裡……你應該離開。錫耶拉馬德雷沒有什麼在等著你。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"I see... You went so far. Like me. Like the Courier, like Dean Domino, like "
"(God/Dog), like Father Elijah... But getting to it... That's not the hard "
"part. It's letting go. Greed, jealously, hate, vengeance, power, control, "
"hunger, money, even love... We all came here for different reaasons... But "
"that's what we had to learn. To let go. Hell, Frederick Sinclair, the "
"Founder himself couldn't let go... And so he himself died in the Sierra "
"Madre... Everyone who left this place learned to let go. The majority "
"didn't... And they all died. Neither could Father Elijah."
msgstr ""
"我明白了……你走了這麼遠。就像我一樣。就像信使，就像迪恩·多米諾，就像(神/狗)，就像以利亞神父……但到達那裡……那並不難。難的是放手。貪婪、嫉妒、仇恨、復仇、權力、控制、飢餓、金錢，甚至愛情……我們來到這裡都有不同的原因……但這就是我們必須學會的。學會放手。見鬼，弗雷德裡克·辛克萊，創始人自己都無法放手……所以他本人死在了錫耶拉馬德雷……離開這個地方的人都學會了放手。大多數人沒有……而他們都死了。以利亞神父也沒能做到。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"That collar on my neck... I have to obey Father Elijah. One of the "
"inscriptions on the villa wall says \"Try to leave and BOOM\"..."
msgstr "我脖子上的那個項圈……我必須服從以利亞神父。別墅牆上的銘文之一寫著“試圖離開就會BOOM”……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"I entered the Casino only because of the guidance of the voice that spoke to"
" me through the fountain hologram and Casino intercom at the lobby... We "
"both know to whom this voice belongs at this point, am I right?"
msgstr "我進入賭場，僅僅是因為那個通過噴泉全息影像和賭場大廳對講機對我說話的聲音的指引……我們都知道這個聲音此刻屬於誰，對吧？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"The Courier managed to enter the vault... And learned to let go. (Dog/God) "
"was a savage mutant with double personality disorder... One was an ever-"
"hungry monster, the other was a power-thirsty narcissist... But the "
"Courier... The Courier had patience both for Dog and God, merging two "
"personalities into one, gentle and peaceful... Dean Domino, that asshole... "
"Even he finally let go and just left the Sierra Madre... And I... I stayed. "
"I need to protect the outer world from the horrors of this doomed place... "
"And Father Elijah..."
msgstr ""
"信使設法進入了金庫……並學會了放手。(狗/神)是一個患有雙重人格障礙的野蠻變種人……一個是永遠飢餓的怪物，另一個是渴求權力的自戀狂……但信使……信使對狗和神都有耐心，將兩個人格融合成一個，溫和而平靜……迪恩·多米諾，那個混蛋……就連他最終也放手了，只是離開了錫耶拉馬德雷……而我……我留了下來。我需要保護外面的世界，免受這個註定毀滅之地的恐怖……還有以利亞神父……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid "So, what happened to the Father Elijah?"
msgstr "那麼，以利亞神父後來怎麼樣了？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid "Alright, I have some more questions."
msgstr "好吧，我還有一些問題。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"He forced the Courier to unlock the vault and disengage its security "
"protocols for him... Then confronted him down there... Wanted to kill the "
"Courier like throwing away a disposable tool once the job is done and claim "
"Madre for himself alone... But the Courier was smart and outmaneouvered "
"Elijah, reached the exit and locked him in the vault from the inside... He "
"must have survived down there till this very moment we're talking right now."
" That's the main reason why I'm here. And I'm going to stay, whether he's "
"already dead or still alive down there, I'll be guarding the Sierra Madre "
"and the vault entrance."
msgstr ""
"他強迫信使打開金庫，併為他解除安全協議……然後在那裡與他對峙……想在工作完成後像扔掉一次性工具一樣殺掉信使，獨自佔有馬德雷……但信使很聰明，智勝了以利亞，到達出口並從內部將他鎖在金庫裡……他一定活到了現在，就在我們說話的這一刻。這就是我在這裡的主要原因。而且我會留下來，不管他是已經死了還是仍然活著，我都會守衛錫耶拉馬德雷和金庫入口。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"I'm afraid he's still alive. And on top of that able to communicate with me."
" And force me to do his dirty job..."
msgstr "恐怕他還活著。而且除此之外，還能與我溝通。並強迫我做他的骯髒勾當……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"Holy shit, how could I not notice this earlier? That collar on your neck... "
"He... He's alive... And he's doing it again... Doing what he did to me, "
"(Dog/God), the Courier and Dean Domino... History repeats itself... He's "
"never let go... Alright, if so, you need to finish it once and for all, "
"walking the Courier's Mile down there and once again confront him..."
msgstr ""
"天哪，我怎麼早沒注意到？你脖子上的項圈……他……他還活著……而且他又在這麼做了……對我、(狗/神)、信使和迪恩·多米諾做過的事……歷史重演了……他從未放手……好吧，如果是這樣，你需要一勞永逸地解決它，沿著信使之路走下去，再次面對他……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"Yeah... Unfortunately... The collars... The voice at the fountain... I "
"remember it all... And now you're here, standing in the Vera's apartment, "
"where the vault door has been placed... Alright... There's no choice... You "
"need to get down there... Finish the job... Stop this madman from freeing "
"himself using you in the process and then unleashing yet another apocalypse "
"upon this world... The Cloud, the security holograms, the vending machines, "
"the collars... It's all part of a bigger plan, and that plan ain't nothing "
"good for everything that lives... You need to continue your heist and stop "
"him... But please... Remember... Getting there won't be the hardest part. "
"It's letting go..."
msgstr ""
"是啊……不幸的是……項圈……噴泉旁的聲音……我都記得……現在你在這裡，站在薇拉的公寓裡，金庫門就安置於此……好吧……別無選擇……你需要下去……完成這個任務……阻止這個瘋子利用你釋放自己，然後給這個世界帶來另一場浩劫……毒雲、安全全息影像、自動售貨機、項圈……這都是一個更大計劃的一部分，而這個計劃對一切生命都絕非好事……你需要繼續你的搶劫並阻止他……但是拜託……記住……到達那裡不會是最難的部分。難的是放手……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"O... Okay... I'll go... Enter the vault... Find him... I'll do it... I'll "
"try to... No, I WILL stop him..."
msgstr "好……好吧……我去……進入金庫……找到他……我會做到的……我會盡力……不，我‘一定’會阻止他……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"Take care... Good luck down there... And one more thing! Don't mention my "
"presence here if you happen to speak with Father Elijah through the intercom"
" or fountain hologram before you unlock the vault. Otherwise he'll be "
"prepared. Sure, he'll attempt to kill you, but if he learns that you met me,"
" he'll want to do so as soon as you peek inside, leaving you with no way to "
"prepare yourself."
msgstr ""
"保重……祝你好運……還有一件事！如果你在打開金庫前，碰巧通過對講機或噴泉全息影像與以利亞神父交談，不要提及我在這裡。否則他會有所準備。當然，他會試圖殺你，但如果他知道你見過我，他會想在你一探頭就動手，讓你沒有時間準備。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"Okay, I will... And I won't. Wish me luck. The vault of the Sierra Madre "
"Casino, here I come..."
msgstr "好的，我會的……而且我不會。祝我好運吧。錫耶拉馬德雷賭場的金庫，我來了……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid "Have you dealt with Father Elijah? Please, hurry!"
msgstr "你處理掉以利亞神父了嗎？請快點！"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid "Still working to get inside..."
msgstr "還在努力進去……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid "Yeah... I went down there, he gave me no choice..."
msgstr "是的……我下去了，他給了我別無選擇……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"So that means that it's truly over now... But I'll continue my watch "
"regardless. To warn those who'll come after you, to protect them from their "
"own greed... Now the best thing you can do is to simply leave. Let go and "
"begin again, beyond those walls..."
msgstr ""
"所以這意味著現在真的結束了……但無論如何，我會繼續守望。為了警告那些繼你之後而來的人，保護他們免受自身貪婪的傷害……現在你能做的最好的事就是離開。放手，重新開始，在那堵牆之外……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json .\npcs\dialogue_console.json
#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#: .\npcs\dialogue_christine.json
msgid ""
"Why are you still here? There's nothing for you in the Sierra Madre. Let go "
"and begin again..."
msgstr "你為什麼還在這裡？錫耶拉馬德雷沒有你要的東西。放手，重新開始……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_console.json
msgid "Sierra Madre control network"
msgstr "錫耶拉馬德雷控制網絡"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_console.json
msgid "Vera Keyes"
msgstr "薇拉·凱斯"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_console.json
msgid "Vera"
msgstr "薇拉"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_console.json
msgid "Holodisk extracted. File not found..."
msgstr "全息磁盤已提取。文件未找到……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_console.json
msgid "Back"
msgstr "返回"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_console.json
msgid "Important! Vera, read..."
msgstr "重要！薇拉，請讀……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_console.json
msgid "To Vera"
msgstr "致薇拉"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_console.json
msgid ""
"Vera, if you're reading this, my fears have come to pass, and this is an "
"apology. I hope you realized what my last words meant to you. If so, they "
"have led you here, and this place will keep you safe. I know what they meant"
" for me, and I fear they have trapped me here. I have extracted the previous"
" entry after our conversation tonight. It can't have been easy for you, and "
"I am sorry for all I've put you through in silence. I know while you do not "
"love me, you did not mean any malice in what you did. I knew about your "
"plans to rob the casino with Dean before you told me. Hearing it from you "
"didn't make it any easier. For what it's worth, I am glad you told me "
"yourself, and I understood the tapes he had in his possession. I do not "
"think either one of you realized what your addiction stemmed from, however, "
"and that is the tragedy in this. I suspect the world would not have believed"
" you, regardless, so I respect your desire to keep it from others."
msgstr ""
"薇拉，如果你讀到這些，我的恐懼已成真，這是一封致歉信。我希望你明白我最後的話語對你意味著什麼。若果真如此，它們將你引至此地，而這裡會保你安全。我知道它們對我意味著什麼，而我擔心它們已將我困於此。在今晚我們交談後，我取出了之前的記錄。這對你來說一定不易，我為我在沉默中讓你承受的一切感到抱歉。我知道你雖不愛我，但你所作所為並無惡意。在你告訴我之前，我就已得知你與迪恩計劃搶劫賭場。親耳聽你說出並未讓事情變得輕鬆。無論如何，我很高興你親口告訴我，我也理解他手中持有的那些錄音帶。然而，我認為你們倆都未意識到你們的成癮源於何處，而這正是悲劇所在。我懷疑世人無論如何都不會相信你，所以我尊重你向他人隱瞞此事的意願。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_console.json
msgid ""
"When first building this Villa, this Casino, I meant it for you. As the "
"world seemed to race headlong towards war, it became part of my desire to "
"protect you. The loans, the funding I poured into the casino's "
"construction... I knew it would not matter when war came for us. It was my "
"means of creating a shelter, a defense if the world was bombarded in "
"radiation and bombs. When Dean revealed his plans inadvertently through our "
"introduction, I realized what had happened, and how I had been tricked. For "
"a time, my thoughts were dark. I changed the casino vault from a shelter to "
"a trap, as I knew the first one to enter would be Dean. He would die down "
"here, and it would have been by his own hand. I fear, however, that I "
"overstepped myself, and the only safe place in the casino is the Vault. I "
"have tried to rewire the systems, change the protocols, and I cannot. I will"
" do one last check on the pipes by the edge of the outside platform and see "
"if anything can be done. I fear it is useless. If you come down here, do not"
" access my personal accounts entry. It contains only a message for Dean, and"
" it will seal the door and you will have no way out - even the elevator is "
"designed to automatically return when the door is closed, and it will lock "
"in place. There should be enough in the Vault to sustain you until help "
"arrives. I have ensured that there is enough medical supplies down here to "
"keep you comfortable. The holograms should defend the casino from any "
"attackers, and the hologram beacon in the Villa will broadcast an emergency "
"signal so that others know you are here. When danger has passed, rescue will"
" come. I hope you were able to read this, and know that I loved you, "
"Frederick Sinclair."
msgstr ""
"最初建造這座別墅、這座賭場時，我是為你而建。當世界似乎疾速衝向戰爭時，保護你成了我願望的一部分。那些貸款、我投入賭場建設的資金……我知道戰爭來臨時這些都無關緊要。這是我創造庇護所、防禦工事的手段，以防世界遭受輻射與炸彈的轟擊。當迪恩通過我們的介紹無意中透露他的計劃時，我意識到發生了什麼，以及我是如何被欺騙的。有一段時間，我的思緒陰暗。我將賭場金庫從庇護所改為陷阱，因為我知道第一個進入的會是迪恩。他會死在這裡，而這將是咎由自取。然而，我擔心我做得過火了，賭場中唯一安全的地方就是金庫。我試圖重新佈線系統、更改協議，但無法做到。我將在外部平臺邊緣的管道上進行最後一次檢查，看看是否還有辦法。恐怕這是徒勞的。如果你來到這裡，不要訪問我的個人賬戶條目。它只包含給迪恩的信息，並且會密封大門，你將無路可逃——甚至電梯設計為在門關閉時自動返回並鎖定。金庫中應有足夠的物資維持你直到救援到來。我已確保這裡有足夠的醫療用品讓你舒適。全息影像將保衛賭場免受任何攻擊者侵擾，別墅中的全息信標將廣播緊急信號，以便他人知道你在此處。危險過去後，救援就會到來。我希望你能讀到這些，並知道我曾愛過你，弗雷德裡克·辛克萊。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_console.json
msgid "Sinclair's personal accounts"
msgstr "辛克萊的個人賬戶"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_console.json
msgid "Warning : private access only. Open personal logs?"
msgstr "警告：僅限私人訪問。打開個人日誌？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_console.json
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_console.json
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_console.json
msgid ""
"Dean, if you're reading this, this is goodbye. You will have many years to "
"read this message. Why you have smiled in my face and held a dagger to me, I"
" do not know. You were rich, respected... even admired, loved by many. When "
"you finally pass away down here, either by your own hand or starvation, know"
" that your greed has led you here, for no reason I can understand. You have "
"made a habit in using others for your own ends. Now, the Sierra Madre is "
"your reward. Whether you used blackmail or force - or even played to Vera's "
"greed, it will not help down here in the Vault. Greed has led you here. I "
"hope it leaves you as empty as you left me. The door has sealed, the "
"elevator has left. Even Vera's voice will not unlock it. Know that on the "
"night of the Gala Event I shall raise my glass and whisper, \"Fortunato\". "
"In pace requiescat, Frederick Sinclair."
msgstr ""
"迪恩，如果你讀到這些，這就是告別了。你將有許多年時間來閱讀這條信息。為何你在我面前微笑卻暗藏匕首，我不得而知。你富有、受人尊敬……甚至被許多人欽佩、愛戴。當你最終在這裡逝去，無論是自盡還是飢餓，要知道是你的貪婪將你引至此地，原因我無法理解。你已習慣為達目的利用他人。現在，錫耶納馬德雷就是你的獎賞。無論你使用勒索還是暴力——甚至利用了薇拉的貪婪，在這金庫中都無濟於事。貪婪將你帶到這裡。我希望它讓你空虛，正如你讓我空虛一樣。門已密封，電梯已離開。即使是薇拉的聲音也無法解鎖。要知道，在慶典之夜，我將舉杯低語：“福爾圖納託”。願安息，弗雷德裡克·辛克萊。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_console.json
msgid "ERROR: terminal locked"
msgstr "錯誤：終端已鎖定"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid "And so here you are, down there in the Sierra Madre Vault..."
msgstr "所以，你就在這裡，在錫耶納馬德雷金庫下面……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid ""
"You've been here the entire time? It wasn't possible for you to enter this "
"vault before me!"
msgstr "你一直在這裡？你不可能在我之前進入這個金庫！"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid "Sierra Madre is mine, and mine alone!!!"
msgstr "錫耶納馬德雷是我的，只屬於我！！！"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid "So what happens next?..."
msgstr "那麼接下來會發生什麼？……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid "So, can I finally get an explanation of what's going on here?"
msgstr "那麼，我終於能知道這裡到底發生了什麼嗎？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid ""
"If you say so... You think you can snatch victory from me like that? You "
"think you're smarter, better?! This ends here, you piece of shit. You were "
"going to get evaporated anyways, just like the rest of the wasteland!"
msgstr ""
"如果你這麼說……你以為你能這樣從我手中奪走勝利？你以為你更聰明、更厲害？！就在這裡結束吧，你這混蛋。反正你也會被蒸發掉，就像廢土上的其他人一樣！"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid ""
"[As you prepare for the final battle, you notice that Father Elijah starts "
"powering up laser turrets positioned around the vault room that you "
"previously missed in the dark. Their charging will take a while, but it's "
"going to be a rather quick one.]"
msgstr "[當你準備最終決戰時，你注意到以利亞神父開始啟動金庫房間周圍你之前在黑暗中忽略的激光炮塔。它們的充能需要一段時間，但過程會相當快。]"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid ""
"You think you're the first one that cracked the Sierra Madre open? Oh no, "
"the Courier did it before you, but then I got betrayed and the Courier "
"trapped me here, leaving the vault, making it lock from the outside... I "
"suspect it's because of the other companions that formed that crew... They "
"had... Bad influence for the Courier, convincing him somehow that I had... "
"Evil plans for them... Though I meant no harm, I planned to release and "
"reward them upon completing the heist."
msgstr ""
"你以為你是第一個打開錫耶納馬德雷的人？哦不，信使在你之前做到了，但我被背叛了，信使把我困在這裡，離開金庫，讓它從外面鎖上……我懷疑是因為組成那支隊伍的其他同伴……他們對信使產生了……不良影響，不知怎的說服他相信我對他們……有邪惡計劃……儘管我並無惡意，我計劃在搶劫完成後釋放並獎勵他們。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid ""
"And that's why you put collars on them, right, and then sent them on a life-"
"threatening mission? That's what \"no harm and reward at the end\" stands "
"for, right?"
msgstr "所以這就是你給他們戴上項圈的原因，對吧，然後派他們去執行危及生命的任務？這就是“無惡意並在最後獎勵”的含義，對嗎？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid ""
"I met one of those \"crew members\" just outside the vault. She's guarding "
"it. She's guarding it so that the outside world won't learn your cruelty. "
"According to her, you can't get Sierra Madre. You should just let go."
msgstr "我在金庫外遇到了其中一個“隊員”。她在守衛它。她守衛它是為了防止外界得知你的殘忍。據她說，你得不到錫耶納馬德雷。你應該放手。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid ""
"So how about rewarding me now? I did my job of unlocking the vault, bot so I"
" could get in and apparently so that you can now get out. I expect a fair "
"share."
msgstr "那麼現在獎勵我如何？我完成了打開金庫的工作，不僅是為了我能進去，顯然也為了你現在能出來。我期待公平的份額。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid ""
"Hold on, not so fast... You think you came here for the legendary Old World "
"treasure, right? The truth is, the real treasure of the Sierra Madre is its "
"technology... Just think of it... Those matter replicators serving as "
"vending machines, capable of providing resources, the holograms for security"
" and winning every battle, the Cloud of toxic gas for wiping up everyone "
"that opposes me, and I can use the collars for the obedience as well... The "
"Sierra Madre can help build or destroy the entire nations... And on top of "
"that is quiet, quiet just like the wasteland should be."
msgstr ""
"等等，別這麼快……你以為你來這裡是為了傳說中的舊世界寶藏，對吧？事實上，錫耶納馬德雷真正的寶藏是它的科技……想想看……那些作為自動售貨機的物質複製器，能夠提供資源；用於安保和贏得每場戰鬥的全息影像；用於消滅所有反對者的毒氣雲；我還可以用項圈來確保服從……錫耶納馬德雷可以幫助建立或摧毀整個國家……而且最重要的是安靜，安靜得就像廢土應有的樣子。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid "You're... insane, completely insane..."
msgstr "你……瘋了，完全瘋了……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid ""
"So... What's next? Is there really no richies inside this vault? Can I... "
"Just walk away then?"
msgstr "那麼……接下來呢？這個金庫裡真的沒有財寶嗎？我……可以直接離開嗎？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid ""
"You've heard the legends of the Sierra Madre... We all have... And so you "
"went to seek its richies... truth is, there's nothing specific awaiting you "
"at the vault. Though it doesn't change the fact that the entire Sierra Madre"
" is a treasure in itself and I plan on utilizing it."
msgstr ""
"你聽說過錫耶納馬德雷的傳說……我們都聽過……於是你去尋找它的財寶……事實上，金庫裡並沒有特定的東西在等你。儘管這並不改變整個錫耶納馬德雷本身就是一個寶藏的事實，而我計劃利用它。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid "What are you going to do?"
msgstr "你打算做什麼？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid ""
"The Sierra Madre technology... Just think of it... Those matter replicators "
"serving as vending machines, capable of providing resources, the holograms "
"for security and winning every battle, the Cloud of toxic gas for wiping up "
"everyone that opposes me, and I can use the collars for the obedience as "
"well... The Sierra Madre can help build or destroy the entire nations... And"
" on top of that is quiet, quiet just like the wasteland should be."
msgstr ""
"錫耶納馬德雷的科技……想想看……那些作為自動售貨機的物質複製器，能夠提供資源；用於安保和贏得每場戰鬥的全息影像；用於消滅所有反對者的毒氣雲；我還可以用項圈來確保服從……錫耶納馬德雷可以幫助建立或摧毀整個國家……而且最重要的是安靜，安靜得就像廢土應有的樣子。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid ""
"The collars, you say? Oh, it was nothing personal... I wish I could just "
"make them cooperate without them, but human nature is what it is, collars "
"were sadly a must-have. Even if they were willing to cooperate, without "
"linked collars they'd end up killing themselves as their greed and the "
"darkest side of human nature were taking over. Yeah, the collars were harsh "
"but a neccessity."
msgstr ""
"項圈，你說？哦，這不是針對個人……我希望我能不用它們就讓他們合作，但人性如此，項圈可悲地成了必需品。即使他們願意合作，沒有連接的項圈，他們也會因貪婪和人性最黑暗的一面而自取滅亡。是的，項圈很殘酷，但卻是必要的。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid ""
"How ironic that some madman like you now starts talking about \"the darkest "
"side of human nature\"."
msgstr "多麼諷刺，像你這樣的瘋子現在開始談論“人性最黑暗的一面”。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid "So, will you tell me at last what's going to happen?"
msgstr "那麼，你終於肯告訴我接下來會發生什麼了嗎？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid ""
"Isn't this entire planet insane since the day the bombs dropped, the dead "
"rose and the aliens invaded? Or maybe it was like that long before the "
"apocalypse, only did we not notice because we were too busy with our "
"comfortable lives? Anyways, I'll use the Sierra Madre to wipe the wasteland "
"clean, to let go of the Old World and then begin again, build a new nation "
"on its aches, a nation free from the burden of the past."
msgstr ""
"自從炸彈落下、死者復生、外星人入侵那天起，這整個星球不就瘋了嗎？或者也許早在末日之前就已如此，只是我們忙於安逸生活未曾察覺？無論如何，我將用錫耶拉馬德雷來淨化廢土，放下舊世界，然後重新開始，在其傷痛之上建立一個新國度，一個擺脫過去重負的國度。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid ""
"So you want to commit a genocide, kill off the remaining survivors, that's "
"what you wanna do? No way this is happening."
msgstr "所以你想搞種族滅絕，殺光剩下的倖存者，這就是你的打算？這絕不可能發生。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid ""
"I've explained everything to you already, and now it's time for you to bow "
"down in front of my superiority... You're of no use for me anymore, you "
"fool!"
msgstr "我已經向你解釋了一切，現在是你在我優越性面前低頭的時候了……你對我沒用了，你這蠢貨！"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_elijah.json
msgid ""
"This world is already in a condition shitty enough to on top of that worry "
"about some maniacs wanting to finish it off. I'll not let you harm any of "
"the remaining surviviors."
msgstr "這世界已經夠糟了，沒空再擔心某些瘋子想把它徹底終結。我不會讓你傷害任何剩下的倖存者。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"Has your life taken a turn? Do troubles beset you? Has fortune left you "
"behind? If so, the Sierra Madre Casino, in all its glory, is inviting you to"
" Begin Again. Come to a place where wealth, excitement, and intrigue await "
"around every corner. Stroll along the winding streets of our beautiful "
"resort, make new friends... or rekindle old flames. Let your eyes take in "
"the luxurious expanse of the open desert, under clear starlit skies. Gaze "
"straight on into the sunset from our Villa rooftops. Countless diversions "
"await. Gamble in our casino, take in the theater, or stay in one of our "
"exclusive executive suites that will shelter you - and cater to your every "
"whim. So if life's worries have weighed you down... if you need an escape "
"from your troubles... or if you just need an opportunity to begin again, "
"join us. Let go and leave the world behind at the Sierra Madre grand "
"opening, this October. We'll be waiting."
msgstr ""
"生活是否陷入困境？煩惱是否纏身？好運是否離你而去？若是如此，輝煌璀璨的錫耶拉馬德雷賭場誠邀您“重新開始”。來到這個財富、刺激與陰謀在每個角落等待您的地方。漫步於我們美麗度假村蜿蜒的街道，結交新友……或重燃舊情。讓您的雙眼飽覽開闊沙漠的奢華景緻，在清澈的星空下。從我們別墅屋頂直視日落。無數消遣等您體驗。在我們的賭場博弈，欣賞劇院演出，或入住我們專屬的行政套房，它將庇護您——並滿足您的每個奇想。所以，如果生活的憂慮讓您不堪重負……如果您需要逃離煩惱……或者如果您只是需要一個重新開始的機會，請加入我們。放手吧，將世界拋在腦後，就在今年十月錫耶拉馬德雷盛大開張之時。我們恭候您的光臨。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"Hey, you! Over there! Can you hear me? Good, I KNOW you can hear me... Now "
"listen closely, listen well... The Sierra Madre, this place... I know why "
"you're here. Your own greed led you here. And now you're going to help me."
msgstr ""
"嘿，你！那邊那位！能聽到我說話嗎？很好，我知道你能聽到……現在仔細聽，好好聽……錫耶拉馬德雷，這個地方……我知道你為什麼來這裡。是你自己的貪婪把你引到了這裡。現在你要幫我了。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "Who's this?"
msgstr "這是誰？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "What was that female voice and that speech?"
msgstr "剛才那個女聲和那段演講是怎麼回事？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "Why should I help you?"
msgstr "我為什麼要幫你？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "Okay, I'll help."
msgstr "好吧，我幫你。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "So, shall we finally discuss more important matter?"
msgstr "那麼，我們終於可以討論更重要的事了吧？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"That was the Sierra Madre broadcasting system... The apocalypse came the "
"same night the Grand Opening should've taken place, so no one turned the ad "
"broadcast off... Since then, it broadcasts the ad across the wasteland over "
"and over, running on backup power... It is what lured you here, am I right? "
"Now, let's discuss more pending topics, shall we?"
msgstr ""
"那是錫耶拉馬德雷的廣播系統……本該舉行盛大開幕式的同一天晚上，末日降臨了，所以沒人關掉廣告廣播……從那以後，它就靠備用電源一遍又一遍地向廢土播放廣告……就是它把你引到這裡來的，對吧？現在，我們來討論更緊迫的話題，好嗎？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"I see you're wearning that metal collar stuffed with explosive charge on "
"your neck... Good. That means obedience. Make the mistake of saying \"no\" "
"and I'll set it off."
msgstr "我看到你脖子上戴著那個塞滿炸藥的金屬項圈……很好。這意味著服從。要是敢說“不”，我就引爆它。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"I mean, of course you don't have to, but if you do, you'll also help "
"yourself cracking the Sierra Madre open. And that's what you came here for, "
"right? So, what do you say?"
msgstr "我的意思是，你當然不必幫，但如果你幫了，也是在幫你自己打開錫耶拉馬德雷。這不就是你來的目的嗎？那麼，你怎麼說？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "I'm not buying into your bullshit."
msgstr "我才不信你的鬼話。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "Okay, okay, I'll help."
msgstr "好吧，好吧，我幫你。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"Alright, it's your choice - but good luck surviving the dangers lurking "
"around every corner here and getting to the Sierra Madre without my help!"
msgstr "好吧，這是你的選擇——但祝你好運，在沒有我幫助的情況下，能活著躲過這裡每個角落潛伏的危險併到達錫耶拉馬德雷！"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "I don't need anyone telling me what to do."
msgstr "我不需要別人告訴我該做什麼。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "Well... Fine, you win, I'll help."
msgstr "嗯……好吧，你贏了，我幫你。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"Have you changed your mind? Did attmepting to get into the Sierra Madre "
"prove to be too difficult for you?"
msgstr "你改變主意了嗎？是不是發現進入錫耶拉馬德雷對你來說太難了？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "I'm telling you again, I ain't helping you."
msgstr "我再告訴你一遍，我不會幫你的。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"It is in your best interest to get down to helping me instead of asking "
"pointless questions. Who am I? I'm just a man who hacked the broadcast "
"system to be able to talk to you. Maybe I'll tell you more, if you prove "
"yourself to be worthy, that is."
msgstr "你最好趕緊來幫我，而不是問些沒意義的問題。我是誰？我只是個黑進廣播系統以便能和你說話的人。也許我會告訴你更多，前提是你證明自己值得。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"Oh, so you can make smart decisions? Good, very good... Now listen: the only"
" way to open the Sierra Madre Casino is to trigger the Gala Event... "
"However, some critical electronics and power distribution systems eventually"
" broke down from lack of maintenance. Fortunately for us, I've learned a lot"
" about those systems and have a general understanding of how they work. I'm "
"aware of three locations around the Villa that should have spare electronic "
"boards and processing units we can use to work around the issues of the "
"failing systems."
msgstr ""
"哦，這麼說你能做出明智的決定？很好，非常好……現在聽好：打開錫耶拉馬德雷賭場的唯一方法是觸發慶典活動……然而，一些關鍵的電子設備和配電系統最終因缺乏維護而損壞。幸運的是，我對這些系統瞭解很多，對它們的工作原理有大致瞭解。我知道別墅周圍有三個地點應該有備用的電子板和處理器單元，我們可以用來解決故障系統的問題。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"The placements of those electronic components were directly linked with key "
"locations for starting the Gala Event and since I know how to start Gala, "
"that means I also know where to find them. I request you to retrieve them. "
"The first Sierra Madre electronic board is located in the power switching "
"station in the Salida del Sol. Remaining two are in the Puesta del Sol, one "
"in the switching station on the corner of the district and the second one on"
" the balcony of one of the buildings next to a wall between Puesta del Sol "
"and medical district. Look at your tracking device, I've marked all three "
"locations for you with green \"S\". Once you get them, go back to the "
"fountain and I'll tell you what's next."
msgstr ""
"這些電子元件的位置與啟動慶典活動的關鍵地點直接相關，既然我知道如何啟動慶典，那意味著我也知道在哪裡能找到它們。我要求你去取回它們。第一塊錫耶拉馬德雷電子板位於薩利達德爾索爾的電力切換站。剩下的兩塊在普埃斯塔德爾索爾，一塊在該區域角落的切換站，第二塊在普埃斯塔德爾索爾和醫療區之間一棟建築的陽臺上，緊挨著牆。看看你的追蹤設備，我已經用綠色的“S”標記了所有三個位置。一旦拿到它們，回到噴泉處，我會告訴你下一步。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "Fine, I'm going..."
msgstr "好吧，我這就去……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "Anything specific I should watch out for?"
msgstr "有什麼特別需要注意的嗎？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"Beware of Ghost People, the mutated former humans that lurk and hunt around "
"the villa. They're dangeorus and even if you \"kill\" them, they'll rise "
"back up after some time. The only way to make them stay dead is to dismember"
" their limbs. Watch out for their traps, too. Also, the entire Sierra Madre "
"is contaminated with toxic gas. There are more concentrated pockets that you"
" should avoid at all costs, but even if you steer clear from them, the gas "
"is still everywhere and will slowly poison your body, so you'd better be "
"quick. Waste too much time, hesitate with your job and it'll kill you."
msgstr ""
"小心鬼人，那些潛伏在別墅周圍狩獵的變異前人類。他們很危險，即使你“殺死”他們，過一段時間他們也會重新站起來。讓他們永久死亡的唯一方法是肢解他們的四肢。也要小心他們的陷阱。另外，整個錫耶拉馬德雷都瀰漫著有毒氣體。有些濃度更高的氣團你必須不惜一切代價避開，但即使你遠離它們，氣體仍然無處不在，會慢慢毒害你的身體，所以你最好動作快點。浪費太多時間，工作猶豫不決，它會要了你的命。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"Also beware of the Sierra Madre holograms. They're a pinnacle of pre-"
"apocalypse technology... Fully autonomous workers... The security holograms "
"will shoot laser beams on sight, however if you'll be lucky to get your "
"hands on the unused emitter and spawn one of your own, it'll serve by your "
"side, protecting you from Ghost People. Also don't waste your bullets - they"
" are simply invincible and the only way to destroy them is to find their "
"corresponding emitters and switch them off. There are also hologram vendors "
"you can trade with, but they're based on pre-war currency, so I wouldn't "
"count much on resupplying this way. However, the entire villa is filled with"
" loot from previous survivors. Also the local vending machines still seem to"
" be working. Using Sierra Madre Casino chips you can easily find in most "
"streets and buildings of the villa you can purchase food from them, and if "
"you find the correct code cards, they'll also unlock military and medical "
"supplies for sale. And one last thing: see that rifle laying right under the"
" fountain? Take it. It'll help you survive."
msgstr ""
"還要小心錫耶拉馬德雷的全息影像。它們是末日前的技術巔峰……完全自主的工人……安保全息影像一見到你就會發射激光束，不過如果你有幸拿到未使用的發射器並生成一個你自己的，它會為你服務，保護你免受鬼人傷害。另外別浪費子彈——它們完全無敵，摧毀它們的唯一方法是找到對應的發射器並關閉它們。還有你可以交易的全息影像商販，但他們基於戰前貨幣運作，所以我不太指望通過這種方式補充物資。不過，整個別墅都散落著先前倖存者的戰利品。另外本地的自動售貨機似乎仍在運作。使用你在別墅大多數街道和建築中很容易找到的錫耶拉馬德雷賭場籌碼，你可以從它們那裡購買食物，如果你找到正確的密碼卡，它們還會解鎖軍用和醫療物資出售。最後一件事：看到噴泉正下方那把步槍了嗎？拿上它。它會幫你活下來。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "That collar on my neck really concerns me..."
msgstr "我脖子上的這個項圈真讓我擔心……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "Alright, I'll pay attention to what you've said... I'm on my way."
msgstr "好吧，我會注意你說的話……我這就出發。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"Oh, no need to worry about it, as long as you obey my orders, that is. The "
"Sierra Madre speakers and radios broadcasted on frequencies that'd set it "
"off by an accident, but the Courier blasted all of them away, so no need to "
"worry about it. Again, as long as you don't tinker with it on your own and "
"obey my orders, this thing ain't gonna blow up. The choice is yours..."
msgstr ""
"哦，不必擔心，只要你聽從我的命令就行。馬德雷山脈的揚聲器和收音機曾以會意外觸發它的頻率廣播，但信使把它們全炸掉了，所以不用擔心。再說一遍，只要你不自己亂動並服從我的命令，這東西就不會爆炸。選擇權在你……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "The Courier?"
msgstr "信使？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"Well, it's not like I feel any better about it, but seems like I DON'T have "
"a choice... I'll be on my way."
msgstr "唉，我也沒覺得好受多少，但看來我別無選擇……我這就出發。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"Oh, nevermind, the Courier was a survivor and a Sierra Madre Treasure Hunter"
" just like you, don't even remind me of this piece of shit... After all I've"
" offered to the Courier I got stabbed in the back in return... But there's "
"no Courier in the Sierra Madre anymore, so fear not."
msgstr ""
"哦，算了，信使和你一樣是個倖存者，也是馬德雷山脈的尋寶獵人，別再跟我提這個混蛋了……我為他付出了那麼多，結果卻被背後捅刀……但馬德雷山脈已經沒有信使了，所以別怕。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "Have you done what I've asked for?"
msgstr "我交代的事你辦好了嗎？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "Yeah, found all three of them, got all three of them."
msgstr "嗯，三個都找到了，全到手了。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid "No, still struggling with it."
msgstr "還沒，還在努力。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"The Gala event has started, the doors to the casino are opened! What the "
"hell are you doing here! Waiting for the Ghost People to catch up to you! "
"Hurry inside!"
msgstr "慶典活動開始了，賭場大門打開了！你還在這兒磨蹭什麼！等著幽靈人追上你嗎！快進去！"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "I don't see the Gala Event has been started yet, hurry up!"
msgstr "我看慶典活動還沒開始，快點！"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "Okay, okay, I'm trying my best..."
msgstr "好好好，我盡力……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "Okay, okay, I'm running..."
msgstr "好好好，我這就跑……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "Then don't waste my time, move and do as I said!"
msgstr "那就別浪費我的時間，按我說的去做！"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "Okay, okay, I'm going..."
msgstr "好好好，我這就去……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"Good, very good... At least now I'm sure you are capable of staying alive in"
" the Sierra Madre... Now the time has come for you to start the Gala Event. "
"Place the electronic boards you've acquired under the fountain hologram so I"
" can scan them. This will allow me to generate a special access code that "
"can be used to trigger the Gala Event using the backup power systems since "
"the main ones have failed a long time ago. The backup should be more "
"resilient than the main one, so it should work just fine. The terminal for "
"controlling the Gala Event is located on top of the Campanas del Sol bell "
"tower. I marked the spot for you with a yellow \"S\". Once you start the "
"Gala, make a run for the casino. The music and the fireworks will attract a "
"lot of unwanted attention... Good luck out there."
msgstr ""
"很好，非常好……至少現在我能確定你有能力在馬德雷山脈活下來……現在是你啟動慶典活動的時候了。把你找到的電子板放在噴泉全息影像下方，讓我掃描它們。這樣我就能生成一個特殊訪問碼，用來通過備用電源系統觸發慶典活動，因為主電源系統早就失效了。備用系統應該比主系統更可靠，所以應該沒問題。控制慶典活動的終端位於坎帕納斯德爾索爾鐘樓頂部。我用黃色的“S”標記了位置。一旦你啟動慶典，就衝向賭場。音樂和煙花會引來很多不必要的關注……祝你好運。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid "Alright, I'm on my way..."
msgstr "好的，我這就去……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"What are you doing here? Waiting till the Cloud kills you? Or you don't want"
" the Sierra Madre anymore? Whatever the case, now it's too late - I order "
"you to immediately get back to work!"
msgstr "你在這兒幹什麼？等著毒雲殺了你嗎？還是你不想要馬德雷山脈了？不管怎樣，現在都太晚了——我命令你立刻回去工作！"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"Wait a moment, before you go. I... we... hope you've enjoyed your stay. "
"Farewells can be a time of sadness. Letting go... difficult. As a guest of "
"the Sierra Madre, you know that truth more than anyone. Frederick Sinclair "
"believed one's life could be made anew every day, that fortunes were more "
"than the wealth in your hands. Love. Life... family, those to care for, and "
"those who will care for you. To those who know these joys, the Sierra Madre "
"holds little they don't already have. Out in the world, beyond these walls, "
"that is your chance to begin again. I hope you'll return, in happier times. "
"Until then, the Sierra Madre... and I... will hold you in our hearts."
msgstr ""
"稍等一下，在你走之前。我……我們……希望你在這裡過得愉快。告別總是令人悲傷的時刻。放手……很難。作為馬德雷山脈的客人，你比任何人都更明白這個道理。弗雷德裡克·辛克萊相信，一個人的生命可以每天煥然一新，財富不僅僅是手中的金錢。愛。生活……家庭，那些你關心的人，以及那些關心你的人。對於那些懂得這些快樂的人來說，馬德雷山脈擁有的東西他們早已擁有。在這堵牆之外的世界裡，那是你重新開始的機會。我希望在更快樂的時光裡，你能回來。在那之前，馬德雷山脈……和我……會將你銘記在心。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_fountain.json
msgid ""
"Don't waste any more time, go inside the casino! It's what you wanted, it's "
"why you even dared to come here, am I right?... So hurry!"
msgstr "別再浪費時間了，進賭場去！這不就是你想要的嗎，這不就是你敢來這裡的原因嗎，我說得對嗎？……所以快點！"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_gala.json
msgid "Start the Gala Event"
msgstr "啟動慶典活動"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_gala.json
msgid "Authorization error! Gala Event couldn't be triggered. Aborting..."
msgstr "授權錯誤！無法觸發慶典活動。中止……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_gala.json .\npcs\dialogue_vendor.json
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_gala.json
msgid ""
"Playing pre-recorded message for the start of the Gala... Everyone, please "
"may I have your attention -- guests and residents of the Villa alike. I ask "
"you to step outside and look to the night sky, it's the moment you've been "
"waiting for, the reason we're all here. The Gala Event, the grand opening of"
" the Sierra Madre Casino, you are the ones who have made this momentous "
"occasion possible, and for that we thank you. So raise your glass in "
"celebration, let music fill the streets, fireworks light the sky and promise"
" of new beginnings fill your hearts. No matter what your fortune, no matter "
"what your cares -- let go this night and begin again. I suggest you hurry, "
"though; the gates of Sierra Madre are open but only for a brief time. After "
"that the doors will close for the evening's festivities and won't open again"
" till morning."
msgstr ""
"正在播放慶典開始的預錄信息……各位，請注意——別墅的客人和居民們。我請你們走到外面，仰望夜空，這是你們一直等待的時刻，是我們齊聚於此的原因。慶典活動，馬德雷賭場的盛大開幕，是你們讓這一重要時刻成為可能，為此我們感謝你們。所以舉起酒杯慶祝吧，讓音樂充滿街道，煙花點亮天空，新開始的希望充滿你們的心。無論你的命運如何，無論你有何憂慮——今夜放手，重新開始。不過我建議你們快點；馬德雷的大門已經打開，但只持續短暫時間。之後大門將關閉，進行晚間的慶祝活動，直到早晨才會再次打開。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid ""
"And so you've entered the Sierra Madre casino and can look at all the glory "
"of the Old World, even at the brink of its end. Few people saw it before "
"you... No one else will... Thought the same thing I told the Courier and yet"
" somehow here you are... Anyways, let's get down to business, shall we? The "
"heist still requires a lot of work."
msgstr ""
"就這樣，你進入了馬德雷賭場，可以目睹舊世界的輝煌，即便它已瀕臨終結。在你之前很少有人見過它……以後也不會再有人……我對信使說過同樣的話，但不知怎的你還是來了……無論如何，我們談正事吧，好嗎？這次搶劫還需要很多工作。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid "Who's this \"Courier\"?"
msgstr "這個“信使”是誰？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid "Alright, what do I need to do to get inside the vault?"
msgstr "好吧，我需要做什麼才能進入金庫？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid "So this is it... This is really it... Madre's mine mine mine MINE!"
msgstr "就是這樣……真的就是這樣……馬德雷是我的我的我的我的！"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid ""
"Alright, alright, enough of this circus. Stop hiding behind holograms and "
"speakers, show yourself!"
msgstr "好了好了，這場馬戲該結束了。別躲在全息影像和揚聲器後面了，現身吧！"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid "Would I get to know who you are at last?"
msgstr "我終於能知道你是誰了嗎？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid ""
"The Courier... The Courier... I... We... We planned and executed this heist "
"together. Along with three other survivors, but the other three... They "
"lacked the skills, they weren't that useful, you know? But the Courier... "
"The Courier could have gotten the Sierra Madre together with me, but the "
"greed... Oh, the greed consumed the Courier's soul... I barely survived the "
"betrayal... But enough of this! The Courier is gone, let's focus on the "
"heist, we're so close!"
msgstr ""
"信使……信使……我……我們……我們一起策劃並執行了這次搶劫。還有另外三個倖存者，但其他三個……他們缺乏技能，沒什麼用，你懂嗎？但信使……信使本可以和我一起得到馬德雷山脈，但貪婪……哦，貪婪吞噬了信使的靈魂……我差點在背叛中喪生……但夠了！信使已經不在了，我們專注於搶劫吧，我們離成功很近了！"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid ""
"Don't lie to me. One of the three other \"useless\" survivors, Dean Domino "
"himself, left his journal in the villa. The Courier saved his life, while it"
" was you being the evil one here all along, Father Elijah!"
msgstr "別騙我了。另外三個“沒用”的倖存者之一，迪恩·多米諾本人，在別墅裡留下了他的日記。信使救了他的命，而你才是那個一直以來的惡人，以利亞神父！"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid "What happened to the other survivors?"
msgstr "其他倖存者怎麼樣了？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid "Fair enough."
msgstr "有道理。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid ""
"Enough is enough, they were bad candidates... All driven by greed, hunger, "
"thirst for power, jealously, vengeance... All survived, all left Sierra "
"Madre, despite none of them being able to let go. Again, enough is enough, "
"let's focus on your task, shall we?"
msgstr ""
"夠了就是夠了，他們都是糟糕的人選……全都被貪婪、飢渴、權力慾、嫉妒、復仇所驅使……所有人都活了下來，都離開了馬德雷山脈，儘管他們中沒有一個人能真正放下。再說一遍，夠了就是夠了，讓我們專注於你的任務，好嗎？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid "Alright, let's crack the Sierra Madre open!"
msgstr "好吧，讓我們撬開馬德雷山脈！"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid ""
"Don't lie to me. One of the three other \"bad candidates\", Dean Domino "
"himself, left his journal in the villa. The Courier saved his life, while it"
" was you being the evil one here all along, Father Elijah! And after all "
"this you dare to say that it's them who \"failed to let go?\""
msgstr ""
"別對我撒謊。另外三個“糟糕人選”之一，迪恩·多米諾本人，把他的日記留在了別墅裡。信使救了他的命，而你，以利亞神父，才是這裡一直以來的惡人！在這之後，你竟敢說他們“沒能放下”？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid ""
"Ahhh, I see... Dean Domino, actor, singer... Thief. Liar. Manipulator. "
"Blackmailer. You don't know what happened in the Sierra Madre the night the "
"portals opened, the dead rose and the bombs fell, do you? Then I suggest you"
" take a look around, the evidence is still laying around here in this very "
"Casino you find yourself in, go see for yourself who Dean Domino truly was. "
"After all, he planned that heist himself as well. He wanted Sierra Madre to "
"be his, his alone... But not even for its treasure itself. He wanted it "
"solely because Sinclair was a happier man than him."
msgstr ""
"啊，我明白了……迪恩·多米諾，演員，歌手……小偷。騙子。操縱者。敲詐者。你不知道傳送門開啟、死者復生、炸彈落下的那個夜晚，馬德雷山脈發生了什麼，對吧？那我建議你四處看看，證據就散落在這個你所在的賭場裡，親眼去看看迪恩·多米諾到底是誰。畢竟，那場搶劫也是他自己策劃的。他想讓馬德雷山脈成為他的，只屬於他一個人……但甚至不是為了它的寶藏本身。他想要它，僅僅是因為辛克萊比他更幸福。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid ""
"Yeah, I noticed those parts in his journal too... Still don't believe you. "
"Him being who he was doesn't suddenly make you a \"good guy\"."
msgstr "是啊，我也注意到了他日記裡的那些部分……我還是不相信你。他是他那樣的人，並不會讓你突然變成“好人”。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid ""
"Be careful with such statements. You've seen the Sierra Madre villa. You "
"know what happened to those who thought the way you do. Their skeletons and "
"desperate wall inscriptions and notes still lay around the streets and "
"buildings... Some killed because they didn't have what it takes to survive "
"in the villa... Most killed each other out of greed though. You don't have "
"to say anything. Just think about it."
msgstr ""
"小心這樣的言論。你已經見過馬德雷山脈的別墅了。你知道那些和你想法一樣的人下場如何。他們的骸骨、絕望的牆刻和筆記仍然散落在街道和建築裡……有些人被殺是因為他們沒有在別墅生存下去的能力……但大多數人是因為貪婪而互相殘殺。你什麼都不用說。好好想想吧。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid ""
"Hahaha, you really think I'm that stupid? You'll meet me... When the time "
"comes. Saw those people around the villa? Or rather what was left of them? "
"Messages full of greed and hate, evidence of them killing each other... And "
"their corpses. All of them, no exceptions. Some preserved their humanity, "
"you might say, as they left stashes of supplies and useful tips on the walls"
" for others, but they were the first ones to die every time the dark side of"
" human nature took over their companions."
msgstr ""
"哈哈哈，你真以為我那麼蠢嗎？你會見到我的……當時機來臨。看到別墅周圍那些人了嗎？或者說他們剩下的東西？充滿貪婪和仇恨的信息，他們互相殘殺的證據……以及他們的屍體。所有人，無一例外。有些人保留了人性，你可能會說，因為他們為別人留下了補給品藏匿點和牆上有用的提示，但每次人性的陰暗面佔據他們同伴的心時，他們總是最先死去的。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid ""
"You owe me an explanation. Remember this. I'm not stupid hence I don't trust"
" you either."
msgstr "你欠我一個解釋。記住這一點。我不傻，所以我也不信任你。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid ""
"So you still don't know? Well, so let it be! We'll talk... If you "
"successfully complete your mission, that is."
msgstr "所以你仍然不知道？好吧，那就這樣吧！我們會談的……如果你成功完成任務的話。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid "Damn you..."
msgstr "該死的……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid ""
"Alright, anything else you feel like wasting time to ask? Or are you ready "
"to proceed with the heist?"
msgstr "好吧，還有什麼你想浪費時間問的嗎？還是你準備好繼續搶劫了？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid ""
"So here's what comes next: the vault is protected by a password... Of course"
" it is, but the problem is, it must be spoken in Vera Keyes' voice, "
"Sinclair's true love... There are three recordings of Vera's songs scaterred"
" around the casino - one in the Tampico, one in the Cantina Madrid and "
"finally one in her own suites on the top floor. Combining them together will"
" yeld the sample of her speech capable of unlocking the door... I've marked "
"the locations of those three recordings for you on your navigation device "
"with cyan \"S\" signs."
msgstr ""
"那麼接下來是這樣的：金庫由一個密碼保護……當然是這樣，但問題是，必須用薇拉·凱斯的聲音說出，辛克萊的真愛……賭場裡散落著三份薇拉的歌曲錄音——一份在坦皮科，一份在馬德里小酒館，最後一份在她頂樓的套房裡。把它們組合在一起，就能得到足以解鎖門禁的她的語音樣本……我已經在你的導航設備上用青色的“S”標記標出了這三份錄音的位置。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid ""
"The catch is, as of now, all three locations are locked behind doors as "
"strong as the entrance you've just opened and walked through. That's caused "
"by the casino's lockdown state cutting out power from said doors. To open "
"them you'll need to go to the power control room and manually restore the "
"power, waking the casino up. Just walk across the lobby to the door leading "
"to the casino area, cross the hall until you reach the storage room on the "
"other side and then go through it to reach the power control room... I've "
"marked it using blue \"S\"."
msgstr ""
"問題是，目前，這三個地點都被門鎖住了，堅固程度和你剛剛打開並走過的入口一樣。這是因為賭場的封鎖狀態切斷了這些門的電力。要打開它們，你需要去電力控制室手動恢復電力，喚醒賭場。穿過大廳走到通往賭場區域的門，穿過大廳直到到達另一邊的儲藏室，然後穿過它到達電力控制室……我已經用藍色的“S”標記了它。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid ""
"Once you're done, bring those three pieces of music here and speak through "
"the intercom. And beware of the security holograms... The Sierra Madre "
"casino is crawling with them, placed in key positions."
msgstr "完成後，把那三份音樂帶到這裡，通過對講機說話。小心安全全息影像……馬德雷山脈賭場裡到處都是它們，被安置在關鍵位置。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid "Got it. Three songs of Vera Keyes."
msgstr "明白了。薇拉·凱斯的三首歌。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid "Have you found the songs already?"
msgstr "你已經找到那些歌了嗎？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid "Yeah, found them, got them, all three of them."
msgstr "是的，找到了，拿到了，三份都齊了。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid ""
"Good, you continue to amaze me... Now combine those recordings in the "
"correct order I'm going to describe to you in a moment and use it to enter "
"the vault... Not sure if you searched Vera's and Sinclair's apartment "
"throroughtfully, but the entrance to the vault is in one of their rooms. "
"Once you're down there... Then... Then you'll uncover everything and crack "
"the Sierra Madre open... Don't let me down, survivor. You've come so far... "
"Good luck, I won't respond on the intercom anymore."
msgstr ""
"很好，你繼續讓我驚訝……現在按照我馬上要告訴你的正確順序組合那些錄音，並用它進入金庫……不確定你是否徹底搜查過薇拉和辛克萊的公寓，但金庫的入口就在他們的一個房間裡。一旦你到了下面……然後……然後你就會揭開一切，撬開馬德雷山脈……別讓我失望，倖存者。你已經走了這麼遠……祝你好運，我不會再通過對講機回應了。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid "Alright, so here we go... The Heist of the Centuries..."
msgstr "好吧，那麼開始了……世紀大劫案……"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_intercom.json
msgid "[The intercom is eerily silent... Nobody responds to your calls.]"
msgstr "[對講機異常寂靜……沒有人回應你的呼叫。]"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_vendor.json
msgid ""
"Welcome to the Sierra Madre. We hope you enjoy your stay. Would you like to "
"buy something?"
msgstr "歡迎來到馬德雷山脈。我們希望您住得愉快。您想買點什麼嗎？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_vendor.json
msgid "Yes, show me your stock."
msgstr "是的，讓我看看你的存貨。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_vendor.json
msgid ""
"We hope you're satisfied with the transaction. Anything else we can do for "
"you?"
msgstr "我們希望您對交易滿意。還有什麼我們可以為您做的嗎？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_vendor.json
msgid "Yes, I'd like to make another purchase."
msgstr "是的，我想再買點東西。"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_vendor.json
msgid ""
"Welcome to the Sierra Madre autonomous vending system. We hope you enjoy "
"your stay. Would you like to purchase something?"
msgstr "歡迎使用馬德雷山脈自動售貨系統。我們希望您住得愉快。您想購買什麼嗎？"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_vendor.json
msgid "Browse the list of available products"
msgstr "瀏覽可用產品列表"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_vendor.json
msgid ""
"Sorry Sir, you don't have enough Sierra Madre chips to buy the selected item"
msgstr "抱歉先生，您的馬德雷山脈籌碼不足以購買所選物品"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_vendor.json
msgid ""
"Sorry Madam, you don't have enough Sierra Madre chips to buy the selected "
"item"
msgstr "抱歉女士，您的馬德雷山脈籌碼不足以購買所選物品"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_vendor.json
msgid "Choose a different product"
msgstr "選擇其他產品"

#: .\npcs\dialogue_vendor.json
msgid ""
"Thank you for using our services. Here's the list of available products for "
"you:"
msgstr "感謝使用我們的服務。以下是可供您選擇的商品列表："

#: .\npcs\dialogue_vendor.json
msgid "Mac & cheese [20 chips]"
